---
source: crates/cosmon-cli/tests/peek_snapshot.rs
expression: "render_row(&i, true)"
---
INPUTS
  status:        frozen
  heartbeat:     Active
  has_blockers:  true
  ghost:         true
  drift:         true
  tags:          temp:hot
  whisper_fresh: true

RENDER
  row_kind:       Drift
  label:          drift
  lifecycle_glyph ⚠   style=fg=Red mod=BOLD
  temp_glyph      🔥   style=fg=Red mod=NONE
  whisper_glyph   🫧   style=fg=Cyan mod=NONE

STRIP (what the operator sees)
  [⚠] [🔥] [🫧]
